710917f-a.title: Manhattan: 4th Street - 12th Street
710917f-a.text:
4th Street, south on west side from 324 West 4th Street, north of
12th Street, to the S.W. corner of Bank Street, also showing
329-27 West 4th Street, east side.
May 4, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.

710918f-a.title: Manhattan: 4th Street - 12th Street
710918f-a.text:
327-325-323 and 31V West 4th Street, including both N.E. and S.E.
corners of 12th Street.
The A. & P. store shown in 319, on the S.E. corner, will later move
over to the N.W. corner, its place being taken by a fruit market.
May 4, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.

711155f-a.title: Manhattan: 12th Street (West) - 4th Street (West)
711155f-a.text:
12th Street (formerly Troy Street) at and adjoining S.W. corner
of weat 4th Street, showing 279-2o5 West 12th Street.

P. L. Sperr.

711156f-a.title: Manhattan: 12th Street - 4th Street (West)
711156f-a.text:
12th Street (formerly Troy Street), east from West 4th Street.
July 7, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.

710925f-a.title: Manhattan: 4th Street - 12th Street
710925f-a.text:
4th Street, east side, north from and iwcluding 12th Street. The
